{"tid":2157320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google：香港政府/警察如要索取數據，請你們外交部循外交途徑向美國政府申請先","createTime":"2020-08-15T03:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T06:51:37.000Z","uid":230104,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd13b3a6b019c26a6bf9e45e6bdd8dcfe76b259","tid":2157320,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】港版國安法自6月30日起生效，當中的「危害國家安全」定義仍然模糊，多間外國科技企業均憂慮港府會以此為藉口，截取公司用戶的訊息。Google昨日則宣佈，正式拒絕直接處理港府索取數據的請求，要求當局循外交途徑向美國政府申請取得這些資料，意味香港獲得的待遇將與中國政府同等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGoogle在電郵聲明中宣佈，暫時不再直接處理由香港當局提出的數據要求，表示「按照慣例，美國以外的機構可根據外交程序取得刑事調查所需的數據」，又指Google在港版國安法6月生效後，已沒有產生數據，強調他們一直小心處理任何用戶數據的請求，並拒絕範圍太廣泛的要求，以保障用家私隱。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/EAVS27E3U5EXVH6XWPMWKR7UQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FEAVS27E3U5EXVH6XWPMWKR7UQE%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8anpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=c8bf9479\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FEAVS27E3U5EXVH6XWPMWKR7UQE%2F&h=36711fc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/EAVS27E3U5EXVH6XWPMWKR7UQE/</a>"},{"pid":"2d0f12d1a654a9b471ec560dd8546e27844fa926","tid":2157320,"uid":230104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"Google：香港警察而家=中國公安"},{"pid":"5843a1b3a33f919a63b0965f52f6650d3fcf72d2","tid":2157320,"uid":56610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"Google已犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e1c43091b8fa199d51cb6a86b2acb742e99835","tid":2157320,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:25:47.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980cdffceac39e0962740677bfad774d8afe3ac7","tid":2157320,"uid":118217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2670fbe5def2450b5fbf9edbe1002847e0e994e","tid":2157320,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"豬閪伯格應該唔會跟隨"},{"pid":"8f51bcbcbe65885f0b2a84c04210a42c732c6d6f","tid":2157320,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:27:20.000Z","msg":"中國不嬲都係咁啦"},{"pid":"571e891b31e3e53d45d9c5e44ab24068b68d6f0b","tid":2157320,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"Google 已經干犯協助危害國家安全。應該立即嚴正執法。"},{"pid":"bac9d28da9c94e4d559d434a967ce1b73ee0e69f","tid":2157320,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"571e891b31e3e53d45d9c5e44ab24068b68d6f0b","tid":2157320,"uid":113277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:32:27.000Z","msg":"Google 已經干犯協助危害國家安全。應該立即嚴正執法。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:34:35.000Z","msg":"最好香港警察開第一槍，上香港Google搜捕員工<br />\n<br />\n咁就好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc7f3ea78e3c9ac6939df5595fab21ebd4be25b7","tid":2157320,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}